  <brief_title>Identification of EGFR-TKIs Sensitivity or Resistance Markers in NSCLC May Help in Optimal Patient Selection</brief_title>
  <official_title>Relationship of Polymorphisms and Mutations of Epidermal Growth Factor Receptor and Tyrosine Kinase Inhibitors Responsiveness in Non-small-cell Lung Cancer Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
